she is best remembered on television as eunice douglas on green acres and , for many , for providing disney animated features with their most outstanding and memorable villainess voices , most notably two of the most sinister disney villainesses , lady tremaine , cinderella 's evil stepmother from cinderella , and maleficent , the evil fairy from sleeping beauty .

